{"tid":491902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【盜墓「袓師爺」】身光頸靚 銀行戶口卻1蚊都無","createTime":"2017-12-07T03:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T05:37:43.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3322239ca5b8cf21cdf070a51594f83c43a03246","tid":491902,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"【盜墓「袓師爺」】身光頸靚 銀行戶口卻1蚊都無 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n偷下5.9億紅山文物的姚玉忠，不服一審死刑上訴，遭遼寧高院駁回。他有盜墓界「祖師爺」之稱，行內聲名顯赫，收入豐富，不過他因好賭成性，時常以贓物還賭債，另有綽號「老敗家」。他平時穿著奢華，可是被捕時，銀行戶口裡卻沒有錢。<br />\n<br />\n姚玉忠在1962年出生，55歲，是內蒙古自治區寧城縣人，學歷只有小學程度。據內媒報道，姚玉忠嗜賭如命，輸贏金額在幾百萬元至千萬元不等。有時他賭癮大發，不堪輸錢，還會當場拿出盜墓贓物作抵押物，有一次他在河北某賭場欠下7,000多萬元賭債，他來不及出售文物換錢，直接拿文物作抵押品，原本價值100萬元的文物，都被折算作50萬元，有些更以10萬元一件當場交付，鮮有贖回。<br />\n<br />\n此外，姚玉忠穿戴奢華，經常出入高級酒店，在內蒙赤峰更擁有豪華別墅，手中玩物亦為稀有珍品，其中不乏紅山玉璧等珍貴文物。他賭博時曾對外炫耀，手頭的珍寶就是盜挖而來，但被警方拘捕之後，銀行戶口裡卻一分錢都沒有。<br />\n綜合報道  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171202/57531959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57531959&d=tQLHp1GlwDP%2BhlMP508MGEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=baf6259e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57531959&h=e8b27b91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171202/57531959</a>"},{"pid":"946fab186f62f86447012b3f02cd8c67bbadcda6","tid":491902,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"河北賭場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfc193e57bd3e892d2cd844a1294a49fd3194bb","tid":491902,"uid":316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"d錢唔見得光呀嘛"},{"pid":"c65f9bb400c9e789457a67ad24b718d326d03e71","tid":491902,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"可能個賭場又係自己開既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0282266c0634a2b7b48f492c621add402d2317f","tid":491902,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"icac曾經講過賭場手法"},{"pid":"f18fb80ff876db32f8f71500019a7934cdb75dc2","tid":491902,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"洗清洗剩先去死"},{"pid":"2dfc4ea2a90b00ca67002252e2c24bfbfefba1c2","tid":491902,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"洗乜放係自己到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6a1a1dab521903c86460c056fd84fe8f29f90d","tid":491902,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-04-15/clipping/450/n11a00_t_02_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-04-15%2Fclipping%2F450%2Fn11a00_t_02_03.jpg&h=d75dbc21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97d75898396a49b868591733cf379d16f041c9e6","tid":491902,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-04-15/clipping/450/n11a00_t_02_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-04-15%2Fclipping%2F450%2Fn11a00_t_02_03.jpg&h=d75dbc21&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁似小說既"},{"pid":"3dd9b3768dcd375c9b7f258ae6d30a5405f920c8","tid":491902,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2016-04-15/clipping/450/n11a00_t_02_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2016-04-15%2Fclipping%2F450%2Fn11a00_t_02_03.jpg&h=d75dbc21&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁似小說既</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n摸金發丘咪係一代奸雄曹操所為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據史書記載，摸金校尉起源於東漢末年三國時期，當時魏軍的領袖曹操為了彌補軍餉的不足，設立發丘中郎將，摸金校尉等軍銜，專司盜墓取財，貼補軍用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曹操因軍費困難，設「發丘中郎將」、「摸金校尉」等職，發兵盜掘永城芒碭山（今河南商丘永城芒碭山）的漢梁孝王墓。"},{"pid":"15af82ecb96fbbf72720a575c8318e6daa546989","tid":491902,"uid":143652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"做得偏門點會將錢入戶口呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，人地成個倉都係現金啦，使入銀行咩"},{"pid":"5697b5e859e20d2af6626c397896930ad81cf877","tid":491902,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"呢啲錢入落銀行咪死得仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}